snippet.title: Unknown Number: A First Person Talker | PC Trailer
snippet.description:
#UnknownNumber #godolphingames 
***************************************************************
SUPPORT Confident Gamers: https://streamlabs.com/confidentgamers
***************************************************************

Unknown Number is a voice-controlled game coming to Steam from indie game studio godolphin games in 2022.

In Unknow Number, you as the player help two eco-warriors, Amanda and Ethan, pull off a heist on an oil rig. You will be tasked with solving puzzles and forced to make high-pressure choices by talking, singing, whispering, and shouting seeing that Unknown Number uses only voice commands for just about everything.

Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1692340/Unknown_Number_A_First_Person_Talker/
